# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-04-15 14:26

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:11
translate chinese whitney8_9853ab00:

    # "My phone starts buzzing. Whitney's calling."
    "我的手机开始震动。是惠特尼打来的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:15
translate chinese whitney8_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "喂？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:16
translate chinese whitney8_371e922c:

    # wt "Good morning, [pcname]."
    wt "早上好，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:17
translate chinese whitney8_cf39ea68:

    # wt "I'd like you to come out to my lab today and bring the hoop with you."
    wt "今天请你来我的实验室，记得把那个圆环带上。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:18
translate chinese whitney8_8d1327d7:

    # wt "I'm ready to start doing some tests on it, so hopefully we can replicate your father's experiment and get him back."
    wt "我准备开始做一些测试，希望能复现你父亲的实验，把他带回来。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:19
translate chinese whitney8_b764178b:

    # pc "Okay, where is your lab?"
    pc "好的，你的实验室在哪里？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:22
translate chinese whitney8_c1a287ab:

    # "She gives me detailed instructions how to get to her lab, then I get dressed, grab the hoop from the basement, and drive out there."
    "她详细告诉我怎么去实验室，然后我换好衣服，从地下室拿上那个铁环，开车去了那里。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:25
translate chinese whitney8_f6905d01:

    # "The place is outside of town on a huge plot of land surrounded by trees."
    "那地方在城外，坐落在一片被树木环绕的广阔土地上。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:26
translate chinese whitney8_ce6d4561:

    # "I park in the circle-driveway at the front and walk up a long path towards her house."
    "我把车停在前面的环形车道上，沿着一条长长的路走向她的房子。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:27
translate chinese whitney8_5f67c947:

    # "Another building that looks like a large warehouse rises up above the house on the right."
    "右边房子上方矗立着另一栋看起来像大型仓库的建筑。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:30
translate chinese whitney8_0081cc36:

    # "I pause for a moment on the path. Should I just go up to the door and knock? Should I send her a text or something?"
    "我在小径上停顿片刻。是直接走到门前敲门吗？还是先发条短信之类的？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:31
translate chinese whitney8_a385c5c3:

    # wt "Go through the door and to the right."
    wt "穿过门，向右走。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:32
translate chinese whitney8_e5f3a53a:

    # "Whitney's voice coming over a speaker somewhere startles me and I nearly drop the hoop when I jump."
    "惠特尼的声音从某处的扬声器里传来，吓了我一跳，我吓得差点把铁环掉在地上。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:35
translate chinese whitney8_8c6e41ff:

    # pc "Uh, this door?"
    pc "呃，是这扇门吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:36
translate chinese whitney8_b8ea1cfd:

    # wt "Yes that door. It is unlocked. Take the hall to the right. The door is labeled."
    wt "是的，就是那扇门。门没锁。沿着走廊向右走。门上有标识。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:37
translate chinese whitney8_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "好的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:40
translate chinese whitney8_01cacda4:

    # "I follow Whitney's instructions through the house, to the right, and through a door labeled \"Laboratory.\""
    "我按照惠特尼的指示穿过房子，向右转，走进一扇写着“实验室”的门。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:41
translate chinese whitney8_e26e6e6a:

    # "The lab is different than what I expected. More like a warehouse or a garage, with open windows above letting in air and light."
    "实验室和我想象的不一样。更像仓库或车库，上方敞开的窗户让空气和光线透进来。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:42
translate chinese whitney8_96655b8e:

    # "The equipment in the place is a mix of old stuff that just looks like junk to me, and newer almost futuristic tools."
    "里面的设备既有在我看来像废品一样的旧东西，也有近乎未来感的最新工具。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:43
translate chinese whitney8_c8e63656:

    # "Whitney is working at a computer desk in the far corner, but when I enter, she turns and drives over to me."
    "惠特尼正坐在角落的电脑桌前工作，但当我走进来时，她转过身，开着车向我驶来。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:47
translate chinese whitney8_47d1da62:

    # wt "Hey there, [pcname]. I hope you found the place okay."
    wt "嗨，[pcname]。希望你顺利找到这里。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:48
translate chinese whitney8_3a839832:

    # pc "Yeah, your instructions were very clear. This is all your house?"
    pc "嗯，你的指示很清楚。这整栋房子都是你的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:50
translate chinese whitney8_89ef433b:

    # wt "Well, this is the laboratory, but if you mean the whole estate - yes, it is mine."
    wt "这个嘛，这里是实验室，但如果你指的是整个庄园——是的，是我的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:51
translate chinese whitney8_63dbdd85:

    # wt "Bring the hoop over here and let's take a look at it."
    wt "把那个圆环拿过来，让我看看。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:54
translate chinese whitney8_90255794:

    # "I follow her over to one of her workbenches and put the hoop down on it."
    "我跟着她走到其中一张工作台前，把圆环放在上面。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:55
translate chinese whitney8_5898a369:

    # wt "Wait, what is this?"
    wt "等等，这是什么？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:56
translate chinese whitney8_80491124:

    # pc "Uh, it's the hoop that I found in the basement?"
    pc "呃，就是我在地下室找到的那个圆环？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:57
translate chinese whitney8_7438caab:

    # wt "This is not the hoop that I made for your father."
    wt "这不是我给你父亲做的那个圆环。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:60
translate chinese whitney8_6b348789:

    # wt "This one is similar, but it's not the same one."
    wt "这个虽然相似，但并不是同一个。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:61
translate chinese whitney8_1798e0e8:

    # pc "Then why was this one in my dad's basement?"
    pc "那为什么这个会在我爸的地下室里？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:62
translate chinese whitney8_9167c132:

    # wt "It seems like he might have made this one himself, based on my designs."
    wt "看来他可能是根据我的设计自己做的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:63
translate chinese whitney8_238623a7:

    # wt "But if the one I made for him wasn't there, where is it?"
    wt "可是如果我给他做的那个不在那里，那它去哪儿了？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:64
translate chinese whitney8_0d8ecf6d:

    # wt "It's possible that he took it with him wherever he went."
    wt "有可能他随身带走了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:65
translate chinese whitney8_d4a9aa35:

    # pc "If he took it with him, does that mean that he planned to use it to come back?"
    pc "如果他带走了，那是不是意味着他打算用它回来？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:66
translate chinese whitney8_cc315649:

    # wt "That logic checks out, yes."
    wt "这个推论说得通，是的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:67
translate chinese whitney8_593845d4:

    # pc "There's something that has been bothering me. The instructions seem to show that the user's body has to go through the hoop, but it looks too small to fit through to me."
    pc "有一件事一直困扰着我。说明书上似乎显示使用者必须穿过那个环，但在我看来它太小了，根本穿不进去。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:68
translate chinese whitney8_8fa0e79c:

    # wt "Oh, that's simple."
    wt "哦，这很简单。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:71
translate chinese whitney8_2f70dff7:

    # wt "It expands when you touch it in the right spot."
    wt "只要在正确的位置触碰它，它就会扩张。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:72
translate chinese whitney8_d7dea5da:

    # pc "Oh wow, okay."
    pc "哦哇，原来如此。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:73
translate chinese whitney8_78fb6f94:

    # wt "There's also a small slot here where the diamond goes. There's some carbon traces here, showing that it was burnt out."
    wt "这里还有一个放钻石的小插槽。上面有碳痕迹，说明钻石已经烧毁了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:74
translate chinese whitney8_44a25a7e:

    # wt "Which means your father definitely used this hoop, and it seemed to work."
    wt "这意味着你父亲肯定用过这个环，而且似乎有效。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:75
translate chinese whitney8_4d47a3d4:

    # wt "And there's a memory chip here. This will contain all the data needed to transfer the physical matter, along with the destination."
    wt "还有一块存储芯片。它应该包含传输物质所需的所有数据，以及目的地信息。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:76
translate chinese whitney8_c8667879:

    # pc "So we can see where he went?"
    pc "所以我们可以查到他去了哪里？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:77
translate chinese whitney8_842d0444:

    # wt "That's the idea. Let's check it out."
    wt "正是如此。我们来看看。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:80
translate chinese whitney8_59c6b5b2:

    # "She removes a small memory chip from a slot on the inside of the hoop and takes it over to her computer, putting it in some sort of reader there."
    "她从手环内侧的插槽中取出一个小存储芯片，拿到电脑前，插入一个读卡器中。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:81
translate chinese whitney8_d37d2d91:

    # wt "The destruction of the diamond must have damaged the chip. A lot of the data here is corrupted."
    wt "钻石的毁坏肯定损坏了芯片。这里有很多数据都已损坏。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:82
translate chinese whitney8_4291afda:

    # pc "So you can't get anything from it?"
    pc "所以你无法从中获取任何信息吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:83
translate chinese whitney8_00f46efa:

    # wt "I think I can, but it's going to take me some time to dig through all of this."
    wt "我想可以，但要梳理完这些数据需要一些时间。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:86
translate chinese whitney8_01905d70:

    # wt "Yeah, I can do this. I'm just going to have to go in and piece everything back together again."
    wt "没问题，我能行。我只需要深入分析，把所有信息重新拼凑起来。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:87
translate chinese whitney8_943d8aea:

    # wt "Give me some time though and I'll be able to tell you where your dad went."
    wt "不过请给我点时间，等我查清楚了，就能告诉你你父亲去了哪里。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:88
translate chinese whitney8_7ef52d77:

    # pc "That's great. Thank you so much."
    pc "太好了。真的非常感谢。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:89
translate chinese whitney8_68edfea2:

    # wt "There's nothing else for you to do here now. I'll give you a call once I know something more."
    wt "你现在在这里也没什么事可做了。等我有了新线索，我会给你打电话的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:93
translate chinese whitney8_ca67bf02:

    # wt "I promise I'll call you soon with whatever information I find."
    wt "我保证一有消息就立刻联系你。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:94
translate chinese whitney8_ba67f62a:

    # wt "In the meantime, just try to be patient and stay hopeful, okay?"
    wt "在此期间，请尽量保持耐心和希望，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:95
translate chinese whitney8_a888ee9a:

    # pc "Okay, I'll try. Thank you again."
    pc "好的，我会尽量。再次感谢。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:96
translate chinese whitney8_4c04d2c6:

    # wt "You're welcome. Talk to you soon."
    wt "不客气。很快再联系。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:99
translate chinese whitney8_e92a15bd:

    # "I leave Whitney's lab and walk back out to my car."
    "我离开惠特尼的实验室，走回自己的车旁。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:100
translate chinese whitney8_7f05f195:

    # "I really hope she can find something."
    "我真心希望她能有所发现。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:103
translate chinese whitney8_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "稍后……"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:113
translate chinese whitney8b_492a1c5d:

    # "I'm about to go to bed when my phone starts ringing."
    "我正准备上床睡觉，手机突然响了起来。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:116
translate chinese whitney8b_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "喂？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:117
translate chinese whitney8b_f60f17fc:

    # wt "Hello, [pcname]. I wanted to let you know that I've gone through and repaired most of the corrupted data on the chip."
    wt "喂，[pcname]。我想告诉你，我已经检查并修复了芯片上大部分损坏的数据。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:118
translate chinese whitney8b_a26884b5:

    # wt "I believe that I've identified the destination that your father was sent to."
    wt "我相信我已经确定了你父亲被送往的目的地。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:119
translate chinese whitney8b_51b4a66e:

    # pc "Really!? Where?"
    pc "真的吗！？哪里？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:121
translate chinese whitney8b_55231eaf:

    # wt "46616e74617379204675636b776f726c64"
    wt "46616e74617379204675636b776f726c64"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:122
translate chinese whitney8b_5bb78b12:

    # pc "Wait, what?"
    pc "等等，什么？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:123
translate chinese whitney8b_2f36447e:

    # wt "It's not like any of these universes or possible realities are named. It's all just data. It's hard to explain."
    wt "这些宇宙或可能存在的现实并没有名字。那都只是数据。很难解释清楚。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:124
translate chinese whitney8b_ee97f1fd:

    # wt "The point is that I can target that same location now and transfer something to there."
    wt "重点是，我现在可以锁定那个位置，并将某些东西传送过去。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:125
translate chinese whitney8b_84389a6c:

    # pc "Great! Let's do it."
    pc "太好了！那就动手吧。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:127
translate chinese whitney8b_06785652:

    # wt "Hold on a moment. I told you I wasn't going to help with this unless we were sure that it was safe."
    wt "稍等一下。我跟你说过，除非确定安全，否则我不会帮忙的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:128
translate chinese whitney8b_56ef83aa:

    # wt "Right now I am positive that it's not safe."
    wt "现在我敢肯定这不安全。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:129
translate chinese whitney8b_eff2f8b9:

    # wt "Also, there's something else. I don't think your father intended to go to this destination."
    wt "还有一件事。我不认为你父亲原本打算去那个地方。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:130
translate chinese whitney8b_a2a6fb65:

    # pc "What do you mean?"
    pc "你什么意思？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:131
translate chinese whitney8b_59275be0:

    # wt "I think he made a mistake, or something happened during the transfer. This is not the target that he intended."
    wt "我觉得他搞错了，或者传输过程中出了什么状况。这并不是他原本的目标。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:132
translate chinese whitney8b_93215e54:

    # pc "Does that mean that he's in danger?"
    pc "那意味着他有危险吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:134
translate chinese whitney8b_7ba80d6a:

    # wt "Almost definitely."
    wt "几乎可以肯定。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:135
translate chinese whitney8b_6b8a4220:

    # pc "Then we have to help him."
    pc "那我们必须去救他。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:137
translate chinese whitney8b_39eb2bc6:

    # wt "We will."
    wt "我们会去的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:138
translate chinese whitney8b_a99ca9b8:

    # wt "Now that I know where he went, I'm going to start working on repairing the hoop, as it was damaged during the transfer."
    wt "既然已经知道他去了哪里，我这就着手修复那个环，因为它在转移过程中受损了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:139
translate chinese whitney8b_4e8b893c:

    # wt "Give me a few more days. I'll call you again with an update soon."
    wt "再给我几天时间。我会很快再给你打电话汇报进展。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:140
translate chinese whitney8b_46e89e6b:

    # pc "Okay, Whitney. Thank you."
    pc "好的，惠特尼。谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:141
translate chinese whitney8b_6dff3d08:

    # wt "You're welcome. Talk to you again soon."
    wt "不客气。很快再联系。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:144
translate chinese whitney8b_fbbc3740:

    # "I hang up and get ready for bed."
    "我挂断电话，准备就寝。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:147
translate chinese whitney8b_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "过了一会儿……"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:157
translate chinese whitney8c_9853ab00:

    # "My phone starts buzzing. Whitney's calling."
    "手机开始震动。是惠特尼打来的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:160
translate chinese whitney8c_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "喂？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:161
translate chinese whitney8c_58e0c9ab:

    # wt "Good morning, [pcname]. I've reached a point in my research where I need your assistance."
    wt "早上好，[pcname]。我的研究到了一个关键阶段，需要你的协助。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:162
translate chinese whitney8c_801e2e5b:

    # wt "Could you come out to my lab again?"
    wt "你能再来我的实验室一趟吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:163
translate chinese whitney8c_f1d0c30d:

    # pc "Sure. I'll get dressed and head out now."
    pc "当然。我换好衣服马上就出发。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:165
translate chinese whitney8c_864d47fe:

    # wt "Thank you. Just go straight to the lab again."
    wt "谢谢。直接去实验室就行。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:166
translate chinese whitney8c_2c0a751f:

    # pc "Okay, see you in a bit."
    pc "好的，一会儿见。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:170
translate chinese whitney8c_356b5f4c:

    # "I get dressed and drive out to Whitney's lab again, anxious to see what she has found now."
    "我换好衣服，再次开车前往惠特尼的实验室，迫不及待想看看她这次发现了什么。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:174
translate chinese whitney8c_43ebde66:

    # "When I get there, I head directly through the house and into her lab again."
    "到了那里，我径直穿过屋子，再次走进她的实验室。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:175
translate chinese whitney8c_7d3d22ee:

    # "She's working on the computer when I walk in, but then turns and greets me."
    "我走进来时，她正在电脑前工作，但随即转过身来向我打招呼。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:178
translate chinese whitney8c_8a3a0672:

    # wt "Good morning. Thanks for coming out here."
    wt "早上好。谢谢你过来。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:179
translate chinese whitney8c_221b7409:

    # pc "You're welcome. What's going on?"
    pc "不客气。怎么了？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:180
translate chinese whitney8c_06002bcd:

    # wt "I need you to take your clothes off and lie on the table over there please."
    wt "请你脱掉衣服，躺在那边的检查台上。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:181
translate chinese whitney8c_5bb78b12:

    # pc "Wait, what?"
    pc "等等，什么？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:183
translate chinese whitney8c_0a7d798d:

    # wt "I need to get all of your vitals and measurements and it would make things easier without all your clothes in the way."
    wt "我需要测量你的各项生命体征和身体数据，脱掉衣服会方便些。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:184
translate chinese whitney8c_21af9c33:

    # wt "You can keep your underwear on. I have no need of anything down there."
    wt "内衣可以穿着。我不需要检查下身。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:185
translate chinese whitney8c_45e80a89:

    # wt "There's no need to be embarrassed."
    wt "没必要害羞。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:186
translate chinese whitney8c_0ea55049:

    # pc "I'm not embarrassed. Just a little surprised."
    pc "我没觉得尴尬，只是有点惊讶。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:189
translate chinese whitney8c_e78ac241:

    # "I strip down and lie on the examination table, feeling rather awkward. She pulls a machine down over my head and turns it on with a sort of buzzing noise."
    "我脱光衣服躺在检查台上，感觉相当别扭。她把一台机器架在我头上，一开机就发出嗡嗡的响声。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:190
translate chinese whitney8c_0389d7fb:

    # pc "What is this thing?"
    pc "这是什么东西？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:191
translate chinese whitney8c_c66baa47:

    # wt "It's sort of like a CAT scan. It's going to measure your brain patterns so that we can store them in the hoop."
    wt "有点像CT扫描。它会测量你的脑电波，这样我们就能把数据存储在环中。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:192
translate chinese whitney8c_c2eb693e:

    # pc "It's not going to give me cancer or anything?"
    pc "这不会让我得癌症之类的吧？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:193
translate chinese whitney8c_48b9eb7c:

    # wt "No, I don't think so."
    wt "不，我想不会。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:194
translate chinese whitney8c_85b1d295:

    # "She spends the next half hour examining me in a very scientific way, obviously not feeling the awkwardness."
    "接下来的半小时里，她以非常科学的方式检查我，显然完全没有感到尴尬。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:195
translate chinese whitney8c_be8b4783:

    # "She takes my blood pressure, a blood sample, swabs my mouth, and asks me for my entire medical history."
    "她给我量了血压，抽了血样，取了口腔拭子，还询问了我完整的病史。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:198
translate chinese whitney8c_a8560158:

    # "Eventually, she is done."
    "最后，她检查完毕。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:199
translate chinese whitney8c_e04a7994:

    # wt "Your body is in great condition physically."
    wt "你的身体状况非常好。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:200
translate chinese whitney8c_e8f490d9:

    # wt "I believe you could make the transition."
    wt "我相信你能完成这次转变。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:201
translate chinese whitney8c_91eec677:

    # pc "You mean, going through the hoop?"
    pc "你是说，穿过那个圆环？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:202
translate chinese whitney8c_fcfdd53c:

    # wt "That is what we're trying to do, right?"
    wt "这不正是我们要做的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:203
translate chinese whitney8c_1f52f549:

    # wt "Send you through to bring your father back?"
    wt "把你送过去把你父亲带回来？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:204
translate chinese whitney8c_42085f5f:

    # pc "Yes, I guess so. It just feels so strange. Like a weird fantasy or something. I still can't believe this is real."
    pc "是的，我想是这样。只是感觉太奇怪了。就像某种离奇的幻想。我还是不敢相信这是真的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:205
translate chinese whitney8c_ecc33c25:

    # wt "We'll take every precaution possible before we do it. I want to make sure you're safe."
    wt "在行动前我们会采取一切可能的预防措施。我要确保你的安全。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:206
translate chinese whitney8c_fdc5f0f0:

    # pc "Yeah, me too."
    pc "嗯，我也是。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:207
translate chinese whitney8c_c53f513a:

    # wt "Okay, you can put your clothes on now."
    wt "好了，你可以穿上衣服了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:210
translate chinese whitney8c_c637416c:

    # "I do as she says and put my clothes back on."
    "我照她说的把衣服穿好。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:211
translate chinese whitney8c_76970b11:

    # "I can't help but feel her staring at me while I do so, this time in a less professional way than she had looked at me before."
    "穿衣服时，我总觉得她在盯着我看，这次的眼神比之前那种职业化的眼神要更不拘礼节。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:215
translate chinese whitney8c_87e35479:

    # wt "Thanks for your help today. I know it was a bit awkward for you, but the data I gathered will help us immensely."
    wt "谢谢你今天的帮忙。我知道这对你来说有点尴尬，但我收集到的数据对我们帮助极大。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:216
translate chinese whitney8c_b3957c4b:

    # wt "I'll use it to configure the hoop to your particular physiology."
    wt "我会用这些数据把传送门调整到适合你生理特征的状态。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:217
translate chinese whitney8c_1a8be2aa:

    # wt "Then my study will shift into finding a way for you to get back home once you have transitioned through the hoop."
    wt "然后我的研究将转向寻找一种方法，让你在穿过传送门后能顺利回到家。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:218
translate chinese whitney8c_7b45e859:

    # wt "Meanwhile, you must play the waiting game again. I'll let you know if I discover anything new or need you for anything else."
    wt "与此同时，你必须再次耐心等待。如果我有什么新发现或者还需要你帮忙，我会通知你的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:219
translate chinese whitney8c_1cb92faa:

    # wt "You may not hear from me for a while, but trust that I'm working on this."
    wt "接下来一段时间你可能听不到我的消息，但请相信我一直在为此努力。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:220
translate chinese whitney8c_3cf430d2:

    # pc "Okay. Thank you Whitney. I'm glad you're here to help me with this."
    pc "好的。谢谢你，惠特尼。很高兴你能来帮我解决这件事。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:222
translate chinese whitney8c_aabc7829:

    # wt "It's no problem. I feel a little responsible for all of it."
    wt "没关系。我觉得自己对这一切多少有些责任。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:223
translate chinese whitney8c_26af9036:

    # pc "Well, just know that I don't blame you."
    pc "嗯，你只要知道我没有怪你就好了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:225
translate chinese whitney8c_070d2d8b:

    # wt "Thank you. That does mean a lot."
    wt "谢谢。这对我来说意义重大。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:227
translate chinese whitney8c_4dfa259f:

    # wt "I'll talk to you later, okay?"
    wt "我们稍后再聊，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:228
translate chinese whitney8c_44ea8ace:

    # pc "Okay. Talk to you later."
    pc "好的。稍后见。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:231
translate chinese whitney8c_939d2065:

    # "I leave Whitney's lab and go back out to the car, hoping that she'll be able to figure this out and we can bring my dad home."
    "我离开惠特尼的实验室，回到车里，希望她能搞定这件事，让我们能把爸爸接回家。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:4
    old "After you meet Whitney in the park, you can call her and talk to her. Ask her if she lives in Skyhill."
    new "在公园见到惠特尼之后，你可以给她打电话聊聊。问问她是不是住在斯凯希尔。"

    # game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney8.rpy:5
    old "Then, a few days later, she will call you and ask you to come to her lab. She'll call you a couple more times over the next few days."
    new "然后，过几天，她会打电话给你，让你去她的实验室。接下来的几天里，她还会再打几次电话给你。"

